*Limbu (ten afenidades culas Kiranti Oucidentales)
;Kiranti Ourientales
*Grande Yakkha''':''' [[léngua yakkha|Yakkha]], [[léngua phangduwali |Phangduwali]], [[léngua belhare |Belhare]], [[léngua athpare |Athpare]], [[léngua chintang |Chintang]], [[léngua chulung |Chulung]]
*Alto riu Arun''':''' [[léngua yamphu |Yamphu]], [[léngua lohorung |Lohorung]], [[léngua meohang |Meohang]], [[léngua waling |Waling]]
; Kiranti Centrales
*Khambu (Rai)''':''' [[léngua kulung |Kulung]], [[léngua nachering |Nachering]], [[léngua sampang |Sampang]], [[léngua saan |Saan]]
*Sul''':''' [[léngua bantawa |Bantawa]], [[léngua puma |Puma]], [[léngua chamling |Chamling]], [[léngua dungmali |Dungmali]]
; Kiranti Oucidentales
*Meio-oeste''':''' [[léngua  thulung |Thulung]] (possible purmeiro galho de las Kiranti)
*Chaurasiya''':''' [[léngua wambule |Wambule]], [[léngua jerung |Jerung]]
*Alto riu Dudhkosi''':''' [[léngua khaling |Khaling]], [[léngua dumi |Dumi]], [[léngua kohi |Kohi]]
*Noroiste (Sunwari)''':''' [[léngua bahing |Bahing]], [[léngua sunuwar |Sunuwar]], [[léngua wayu |Wayu]]
==Berbos==
Ls berbos de l Kiranti nun son facilmente segmentables an funçon percipalmente de la grande persença de palabras [[palabra-balise|balise]]s, a muitos [[afixo]]s sequenciados i tamien de muita [[alomorfia]] por bezes nun antuitiba.
